INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `author_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `seo_title`, `excerpt`, `body`, `image`, `slug`, `meta_description`, `meta_keywords`, `status`, `featured`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(5, 22, 1, 'Becoming Relevant in Today\'s world Part 1', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Let&rsquo;s examine the world we are into today. Everybody is having one need/challenge/problem or the other. Some need more income for sustainability, some need advice/lectures on something, and some need one product/service. Here in Nigerian, our education system is not helping matters; sometimes we focus on outdated knowledge.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Technology has been doing a lot in our today&rsquo;s world. Technology has been changing the way things are being done. In today&rsquo;s world, we hear things like crypto currencies, E-commerce, E-education, E-governance, AI, Big Data and so on. Change is always constant. If you don&rsquo;t embrace the current technology, you will be left out.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>The subject we have in mind to discuss is being relevant in our today&rsquo;s world. The knowledge we have in our current system of education in Nigeria is not making us relevant in our today&rsquo;s world. Technology has changed everything, clinging to what you learnt in school will afford you less to be compared to what the society demands from you. The society is interested in what problem you can solve rather than what theory you can memorize. Am not trying to say that schooling is wrong; NO, schooling gives you a foundation on which you can build. The society today has gone beyond foundation level.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img title=\"problem solving\" src=\"https://www.ziksales.com//storage/posts/August2019/problem-solving.jpg\" alt=\"problem solving\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Moreover you might be asking &ldquo;What is the way out?&rdquo; The way out is to gain additional skills. Skills make you able to solve people&rsquo;s problem. The more people you can serve is the more influence and wealth you can have. Let&rsquo;s take an example; if you can serve the education sector, your sphere of influence and wealth will come from that sector alone. You only reap where you sow. If you decide to serve the business sector, your sphere of influence and your wealth as well will increase.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>There are 12 months in a year, you can decide to learn 1-4 valuable skills, professionalize and monetize them.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>Learn valuable skills that are still relevant in this our 21<sup>st</sup> century. You can as well learn valuable skills pertaining to your area of study in school. Solving problems in a particular field is what makes you valuable and relevant in that field. Think of valuable skills you can lay your hands on. <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span>We will discuss on valuable skills, how to acquire them and monetize them in our next post.</p>', 'posts/August2019/wsNwwu3he4Jt3JxcRWFi.jpg', 'becoming-relevant-in-today-s-world-part-1', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-08-01 18:53:32', '2019-08-01 18:53:32'),
(6, 22, 1, 'The Interview Question', 'This is the short story of my Interview', 'This is the short story of my interview', '<div class=\"_2cuy _3dgx\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1d2129;\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"4f9gj\" data-offset-key=\"c7jc8-0-0\">\r\n<div class=\"_1mf _1mj\" style=\"position: relative; direction: ltr; font-family: inherit;\" data-offset-key=\"c7jc8-0-0\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">This is a must read for students and those who want to work in companies. I want to first of all acknowledge God for whom through his grace it was possible.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">I got to this institute that offers digital skills of which I submitted my letter for internship program, later on I went for the interview the following week. My boss asked me what I studied in school and lots of questions of which I answered well but he wasn&rsquo;t that much interested.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">He went ahead to asked if I am good in software development, I replied him that am a web developer. He requested to see some of my works of which he accessed 3 out of my 5 works that are online. From then, the man knew that I am a man of value. He said he will make sure that I get this IT placement. Then we scheduled a meeting with the CEO of the institute, for him to interview me.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">On the day of my interview, my boss met the CEO, I overheard them discussing against bringing in IT students, of which my boss tried to explain some things to him. On hearing that, I wasn&rsquo;t comfortable again, I have to even start praying.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">When the CEO came out of his office to interview me, He asked me one deep question; he said &ldquo;What have you done for your department in school?&rdquo; Fortunately for me, it happened that I developed a website for the department; in the website, students can chat, information dispatched etc. it&rsquo;s more like a portal. He went further to asked which tool I used to build it, of which I listed them for him.&nbsp; After I explained this to him, he went back to his office.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">I started reflecting over that question, and I noticed that the question calls for a sense of responsibility and value. Wherever you find yourself, always have this sense of responsibility, add value to your society. The bible says &ldquo;<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #001320; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">A man\'s gift maketh room for him, and bringeth him before great men.</span>&rdquo; &ndash; Proverbs 18:16. Learn profitable skills that will add value to you and your society even as a student. People might tell you that there is no space for you in their firm, but once they see that you are a man of value, they will accept you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'posts/August2019/ipO6AHuVtLbc9GMhtu12.jpg', 'the-interview-question', 'this is my interview story', 'the interview question', 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-08-24 20:30:25', '2019-08-24 23:51:19'),
(7, 22, 1, 'The Power Of Team Work', 'The power of team work', 'The power of Team work', '<p>The&nbsp; power&nbsp; of&nbsp; Team&nbsp; work.</p>\r\n<p>This a&nbsp; must&nbsp; read&nbsp; for anyone&nbsp; who&nbsp; wants to&nbsp; achieve&nbsp; success.&nbsp; In&nbsp; my&nbsp; work place,&nbsp; I&nbsp; was&nbsp; given a project&nbsp; to do&nbsp; and&nbsp; moreover&nbsp; this project&nbsp; has been&nbsp; there&nbsp; up&nbsp; to&nbsp; a&nbsp; year without&nbsp; anyone&nbsp; attempting&nbsp; to&nbsp; do&nbsp; it.&nbsp; The project&nbsp; was&nbsp; all about&nbsp; converting&nbsp; the&nbsp; company&rsquo;s&nbsp; logo&nbsp; into&nbsp; 3D&nbsp; and&nbsp; then animate&nbsp; it.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Am&nbsp; a&nbsp; web&nbsp; developer&nbsp; and&nbsp; not&nbsp; a&nbsp; graphics designer&nbsp; but&nbsp; my&nbsp; boss&nbsp; won&rsquo;t&nbsp; understand&nbsp; that.&nbsp; I&nbsp; have&nbsp; no&nbsp; option than&nbsp; to&nbsp; accept&nbsp; to&nbsp; do&nbsp; the&nbsp; project.&nbsp; I&nbsp; started&nbsp; my&nbsp; research&nbsp; and&nbsp; I&nbsp; came&nbsp; across a&nbsp; particular&nbsp; tutorial&nbsp; video&nbsp; of which&nbsp; I&nbsp; did&nbsp; what&nbsp; the&nbsp; man&nbsp; taught&nbsp; in&nbsp; the&nbsp; video&nbsp; but&nbsp; I&nbsp; was&nbsp; stuck&nbsp; somewhere&nbsp; and&nbsp; I&nbsp; lost&nbsp; interest&nbsp; in&nbsp; that project.&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>My&nbsp; colleague&nbsp; took&nbsp; interest&nbsp; in&nbsp; the project&nbsp; and&nbsp; did&nbsp; his research&nbsp; and&nbsp; came&nbsp; across&nbsp; the&nbsp; same&nbsp; tutorial&nbsp; video&nbsp; that I&nbsp; used but&nbsp; along&nbsp; the&nbsp; line&nbsp; he&nbsp; also&nbsp; got&nbsp; stuck.&nbsp; We&nbsp; agreed&nbsp; to&nbsp; come&nbsp; together&nbsp; and&nbsp; do&nbsp; the&nbsp; project.&nbsp; It&nbsp; took&nbsp; us less&nbsp; time&nbsp; to&nbsp; achieve&nbsp; that&nbsp; project&nbsp; using&nbsp; the&nbsp; same&nbsp; tutorial video.&nbsp; We&nbsp; approached&nbsp; our boss&nbsp; with the&nbsp; final result&nbsp; and&nbsp; he&nbsp; was&nbsp; greatly&nbsp; impressed.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We are all&nbsp; human, we&nbsp; have&nbsp; this&nbsp; tendencies&nbsp; of selfishness&nbsp; and&nbsp; self-sufficiency&nbsp; but&nbsp; I&nbsp; will ask&nbsp; you&nbsp; to&nbsp; drop&nbsp; it, if it is&nbsp; success&nbsp; that&nbsp; you&nbsp; need. Even&nbsp; in&nbsp; the bible&nbsp; when God&nbsp; saw&nbsp; some&nbsp; men building&nbsp; the tower&nbsp; of Babel&nbsp; he said&nbsp; &lsquo;&rsquo;If as&nbsp; one&nbsp; people&nbsp; speaking&nbsp; the&nbsp; same&nbsp; language&nbsp; they&nbsp; have&nbsp; begun&nbsp; to&nbsp; do&nbsp; this,&nbsp; then nothing&nbsp; they&nbsp; plan&nbsp; to do&nbsp; will&nbsp; be&nbsp; impossible&nbsp; for them.&rsquo;&rsquo;&nbsp; &ndash;&nbsp; Genesis&nbsp; 11:6.&nbsp; God&nbsp; understood&nbsp; the&nbsp; power&nbsp; of&nbsp; team&nbsp; work.&nbsp; You&nbsp; are&nbsp; on your path&nbsp; to&nbsp; success&nbsp; but&nbsp; you&nbsp; can&rsquo;t&nbsp; do&nbsp; it&nbsp; alone.&nbsp; You&nbsp; need&nbsp; the&nbsp; partnership&nbsp; of&nbsp; God&nbsp; and&nbsp; your&nbsp; Team&nbsp; mates. Strong&nbsp; businesses&nbsp; we&nbsp; see&nbsp; today&nbsp; weren&rsquo;t&nbsp; built&nbsp; by&nbsp; one&nbsp; man.&nbsp; Two&nbsp; heads&nbsp; will always be&nbsp; better&nbsp; than&nbsp; one.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', 'posts/August2019/tVBQ5kfU1NWm6OFBMdDX.jpeg', 'the-power-of-team-work', 'The power of team work', 'Team work', 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-08-31 15:37:11', '2019-09-03 16:05:52'),
(8, 22, 1, 'PREMONITION DREAM', 'PREMONITION DREAMS', 'I know you must have had that scary night where you dreamt about a loved one in trouble,a threat on your life, when you failed an exam or you been in a place where you have not gone before in your life,it might be a premonition dream.\r\nEveryone must have had a premonition dream and experienced a déjà vu(the feeling that one has lived through the present situation before).', '<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I know you must have had that scary night where you dreamt about a loved one in trouble,a threat on your life, when you failed an exam or you been in a place where you have not gone before in your life,it might be a premonition dream.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Everyone must have had a premonition dream and experienced a d&eacute;j&agrave; vu(the feeling that one has lived through the present situation before).</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>MY EXPERIENCE ON PREMONITION DREAM</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">The dream:</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I had a dream about my female friend that was married. In that dream she was trying to climb a height with a ladder and I tried telling her to be careful that she might fall,maybe she didn\'t hear me. She fell to the ground and broke her legs; when I woke up I took it as one of those bad dreams.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Though it didn\'t happen the way I dreamt of it and it didn\'t happen that week,it was after two months that I heard that she and her husband are divorced. I kind of like blamed myself for what happened,I thought maybe if I had told her to be careful she couldn\'t have been divorced.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>THEN WHAT IS PREMONITION DREAM</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Premonition dream is a dream that grants you knowledge of things that haven\'t happened yet or a forewarning about something unpleasant that is to happen in the future.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>FACTS ABOUT PREMONITION DREAM</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">1.We might have premonition dreams if their is an immediate threat on our lives or on that of a loved one,and in such situation we can do something to prevent it.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">2.You can\'t demand a premonition dream,but you can become more prone to it by relaxing the mind before sleep.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">3.If a dream is recurrent on the same night it might be a premonition dream.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">4. Period of full moons is the most likely times for people to experience premonition dreams.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">5.Because of family bonds,moms have premonition dreams about their children.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>HOW TO REMEMBER PREMONITION DREAM</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">To remember a dream it is advised for us to sleep with a journal,so as to write down what we dreamt about immediately we wake up. This also applies to remembering premonition dream.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>IMPORTANCE OF PREMONITION DREAMS</strong></div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">1. Since some come to warn us of future failures,so it helps us to prepare in order to avoid such failures.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">2.It can also help us to stay out of dangers on our lives.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I will like to know if you have had a premonition dream before or what you think about the article or if have anything to add pls drop it as a comment.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">EMMANUEL .C. JOSHUA</div>', 'posts/September2019/ZxzZqFyh7BaEQIJo3yQy.jpg', 'premonition-dream', 'PREMONITION DREAMS', 'PREMONITION DREAMS', 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-09-06 02:04:31', '2019-09-06 02:04:56'),
(9, 22, 1, 'How to Place an order online', 'How to Place an order online', 'How to Place an order online', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #1c1e29;\">There is no doubt that most stores are going online, and in this post, I will guide you on how to place your order(s) online. You have to trust the e-commerce website that you are using before you make payment(s). Make sure that the website is SSL protected. What I mean by SSL protected is when the URL of the site is https:// not Http://. When the website is SSL protected, all transactions are encrypted against hackers.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #1c1e29;\"><img src=\"https://www.ziksales.com//storage/posts/September2019/https logo2.JPG\" alt=\"httpss symbol\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"color: #1c1e29; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt;\">There is a standard workflow in placing orders online. The standard workflow goes like this: when you log in to the e-commerce website of your choice, you will see varieties of products. When you come across the product of your choice, click on the product and once that is done loading, you will see the detail(s) of the product. On that same page, you will see a button that says &ldquo;Add to cart&rdquo;. Once you click on that button, the product automatically adds to your cart. Sometimes you will see that the cart symbol at the top of the website has changed. When you clicked the &ldquo;Add to cart&rdquo; button, the website takes you to the cart page where you will see other item(s) in your cart.<img src=\"https://www.ziksales.com//storage/posts/September2019/Screenshot_2019-09-21 SUSPENSO - Container Glass - Ziksales1.png\" alt=\"add to cart button\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"color: #1c1e29; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt;\">There are two buttons that you will most likely see on this cart page. One of the buttons says &ldquo;Continue shopping&rdquo; which means you can add more product(s) to your cart and if you click it, you will most likely be redirected to the homepage where you can pick other product(s) as well. The other button on the cart page is the checkout button. When you click the checkout button, two things are likely to happen, either it takes you to the login page or it takes you to the checkout page. If you are not logged in, it will take you to the login page because the website needs the information of the person that wants to checkout. If you have not signed up/registered in the site, this is where you register and continue with your order(s) but if you are logged in, the website will take you to the checkout page.<img src=\"https://www.ziksales.com//storage/posts/September2019/Screenshot_2019-09-21 My Cart - Ziksales1.png\" alt=\"checkout and continue shopping button\" /></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #1c1e29;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #1c1e29;\">When you are at the checkout page, you will see your detail(s). The order(s) will be delivered to the detail(s) in the checkout page. If those detail(s) are not correct, you can go to your profile page and correct them before continuing with your checkout. At the checkout page, you will see a button that says &ldquo;Pay now&rdquo;. When you click the pay now button, you will be taken to where you will make your payment using your debit/credit card or other methods of payment.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #1c1e29;\"><img src=\"https://www.ziksales.com//storage/posts/September2019/Screenshot_2019-09-21 Checkout - Ziksales1.png\" alt=\"pay now button\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-outline-level: 1;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #1c1e29; mso-font-kerning: 18.0pt;\">I hope this article helped you, tell me what you think in the comment box.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'posts/September2019/7U3AS9uIJc9kOd5zyEDc.png', 'how-to-place-an-order-online', 'How to Place an order online', 'How to Place an order online', 'PUBLISHED', 0, '2019-09-21 18:36:07', '2019-09-21 18:57:58');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `author_id`, `category_id`, `title`, `seo_title`, `excerpt`, `body`, `image`, `slug`, `meta_description`, `meta_keywords`, `status`, `featured`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(10, 22, 1, 'Renegotiate your destiny', 'Renegotiating your destiny by John obidi', 'Renegotiating your destiny by John obidi', '<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I grew up hearing &ldquo;God&rsquo;s time is the best&rdquo;. One day, I searched the Bible for this sentence and it wasn&rsquo;t there.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">A mortal human said it once and it quickly became a popular aphorism mostly amongst those who needed comfort in the face of unending despair.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">While I appreciate the power of patience, I find it impossible to ignore the momentum of will.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I&rsquo;ve found that with the right amounts of courage, creativity, determination and persistence, closed doors cannot hold up for long.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Being born in the lower middle class of Nigeria forced me to explore this in detail.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">We weren&rsquo;t dirt poor per se, but I grew up in circumstances I considered unfair. I was born and gifted with incredible intellect and an uncommon wit, but not an equal chance to compete on my level of intelligence.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Most of my childhood and adolescence (before the Internet), I felt like I was in a prison, unable to renegotiate my position in this world because well, I was still under the care of my parents who were also caught in the web of lack and debt themselves.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">As a child, my escape from this prison was to daydream and reimagine my position in the world.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">This was why my favourite Shakespearean story (despite its tragic end) was OTHELLO - the negro soldier who &lsquo;bought back his equality&rsquo; through excellence.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">When I was 7 years old, my Primary 3 teacher once summoned my parents to school to ask if there were problems at home because I was often absentminded and detached from the other kids.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I still remember her face and her name, the eternally sweet Miss Adade. While she would be teaching, I would look out the window and drift away in thought. I would dream of the worlds I&rsquo;d read about in books and write myself into their stories.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">She was right in assuming that I was troubled, but wrong in thinking it was because of my parents&rsquo; bickering. Other kids were affected by that sort of thing, but I was pulled by something else.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Like a young, skinny Cassius Marcellus Clay from Louisville, Kentucky who believed he was destined to be Muhammad Ali, The Greatest of All Time; Or a Jesus of Galilee who was convinced of his divine destiny to change the world outside of his hometown.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I knew I didn&rsquo;t have to take &lsquo;this&rsquo;. The &lsquo;how&rsquo; was a Science I was determined to figure out.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">She made me stay behind after school one day and grilled me to find out the problem. She was certain my parents had problems.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">What was this woman&rsquo;s problem? I always aced my subjects with little effort. Just let me daydream in peace. It&rsquo;s not like I threatened to blow up the school.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I didn&rsquo;t know how to explain what was going on in my head so I admitted that my parents were indeed quarrelling so she&rsquo;d let me go back to my daydreaming.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I made it believable too. That was the day I learned to cry on demand. Lol. She eventually moved my seating position from the window to the middle row at the front where she could watch me. Whenever I drifted again, she&rsquo;d call me to her desk to help her mark scripts.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My parents did quarrel from time to time, but it was nothing that low-income couples didn&rsquo;t go through in that time. The lack of money was the root of all shenanigans.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Oh well...&nbsp; I kept on getting tossed by circumstances I couldn&rsquo;t control until I turned 17. That was when I got shipped off to the University of Port Harcourt where I met my first in-person role model - Uyi Ebhuoma.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Oh, the sweet smell of freedom. For the first time in my life, I felt like the keys to my life was handed to me. Here, I would figure out how to claw my way up to where I knew I deserved to be.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I was walking into my hostel (on Choba campus) one afternoon and saw an ad on the notice board. It said &ldquo;Learn Website Design at 500 Naira. Contact Uyi at Room *something*&rdquo;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I went there to find him. He paid for &lsquo;all night browsing&rsquo; at the then Net Express cyber cafe and in 2 days, Uyi taught me Website Design in exchange for 300 Naira only.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My mind exploded and you can bet I spent more time in school than I did at home.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">However, my time in Uniport had to end. Third world shackles tried to hold me down through the broken Nigerian public education system.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I wanted to study Computer Science but the &lsquo;system&rsquo; decided I was to study Physics.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I knew clearly, what my path was to be. Who the hell was a mostly corrupt human-constituted government agency to decide the course of my life?&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">While many didn&rsquo;t mind (and some thrived in) the public schooling system, it was killing my spirit. It wasn&rsquo;t my path.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">After 2 years, I made a compelling, dramatic and exaggerated case to my parents and uncles (who were paying my fees) and they let me transfer to Benson Idahosa University in 2005.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I had just turned 19 when I arrived in BIU, Benin City.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">BIU was a merit-based Private University led by its President, Bishop F.E.B. Idahosa, the son of the late Archbishop Benson Idahosa.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">It was free from most of the corruption that bedevilled the public education system. The first point of entry was the Guidance and Counseling unit were I was welcomed by a woman who looked genuinely happy to see me.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">She asked me what I wanted to study and why.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">What a wawu! I had options?&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I told her I wanted Computer Science because it had been my dream since I was 5 years old.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">She looked at my NECO results and because I had the required grades, I was admitted to the Department of Computer Science. No lobbying, no begging, no bribery, no need for connections - just good old merit.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I didn&rsquo;t have a computer but I was delightfully surprised to see that BIU had a functioning Computer Laboratory, equipped with the latest software and we were allowed one hour of internet access per day. This was where I spent most of my time.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Our courses included Web Design, Computer Networking, C++, Visual Basic and Assembly Language.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I stayed in the lab and practiced to stupor. When I learned that those skills could in the future, buy me even more leverage in the game of life, I pumped up the pressure.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">When I went home on holidays to my hometown of Ibusa, Delta State, I faced another quagmire.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">There was no electricity there but that&rsquo;s where I and my family lived. Refusing to accept my constraints, I took a bus to the capital (Asaba) every day so I could find a cybercafe to charge my laptop and practice my programming.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My life has undergone a number of twists and turns leading up to the present day, but one thing has been constant - I don&rsquo;t take an option simply because it&rsquo;s the only thing on the table.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I&rsquo;ve always tried to renegotiate my position - with prayer, skill, application of wit and force of will.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">From realizing that I had to move to Lagos in 2014 to taking my chances on the international stage in 2018, I know that I must keep moving, bobbing and weaving.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">There are many stories in between but I&rsquo;ll skip them for the sake of brevity.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I&rsquo;m writing this for people who think they must take what life serves, for those who think that just because their lives began a certain way, it must&rsquo;ve been God&rsquo;s will.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I&rsquo;ve heard people say that religion is the problem of Nigerians. They&rsquo;re wrong.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I see the Bible for example, as a buffet. There&rsquo;s so much in there and you can choose your own manifesto.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Some would choose bible verses on patience and waiting on God. I choose the ones on urgency of purpose.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Some focus on the verses that glory in affliction. I focus on the stories of the people who broke through.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Some focus on stories of Cain who was cursed and it remained so. I focus on Jabez who though born into sorrowful circumstances and was named so, renegotiated his destiny.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I focus on the story of Jacob who because of his background as a cheat and his mother&rsquo;s prompting, was condemned to suffer the consequences of his deceit, running in circles with no meaningful progress. The day he decided he had had enough, he wrestled with an angel all night long for a chance to rewrite his fate.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">If you&rsquo;re weak and helpless, you&rsquo;ll find an interpretation that provides you comfort in your misery.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">But if you&rsquo;re the sort that is always looking for and willing to fight for better, you&rsquo;ll find verses and stories that quicken your creativity.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">What verses do you choose? The ones that you can use as alibis for laziness or the ones that trigger your pursuit for more.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">When I tell my stories, there&rsquo;s usually that cynical Nigerian who acts like we&rsquo;re in a suffering competition.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">They&rsquo;d say things like &ldquo;Your own good na. If you hear my own ehn...&rdquo;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Be quiet sah! We are not of the same bloodline.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Your idea of suffering is existential - food for the belly.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My idea of misery is the restlessness from unused potential - knowing what I&rsquo;m capable of, but unable to do due to man-made constraints.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My message to you all is that you keep on renegotiating your position.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Don&rsquo;t accept your circumstances just because a mortal human wrote &ldquo;Man proposes, but God disposes&rdquo;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Don&rsquo;t accept it when people say you must endure a certain lifestyle because it is destiny.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Through force of will, historical figures have renegotiated their destiny.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Jesus said &ldquo;What is bound on Earth is bound in Heaven&rdquo;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I read an Igbo proverb in my father&rsquo;s diary - &ldquo;When a man says yes, his chi says yes also&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Les Brown notably wrote &ldquo;History is being read, but it&rsquo;s also being written by people with imagination&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">My life story is still unfolding but I never forget that I hold the pen. I&rsquo;m not where I want to be yet, but knowing that at every crossroads, I can negotiate my direction and momentum, is in itself a hack.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Are you battling constraints of age, location, finance, health, education, network?&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Muster your courage, creativity, determination and persistence.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">While I appreciate the power of patience, I find it impossible to ignore the momentum of will.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">I remember writing here once, &ldquo;The cards are being shuffled every day, and children of commoners are being offered a shot at first-generation royalty&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Don&rsquo;t take it as it is.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Through prayer, skill, application of wit and force of will, RENEGOTIATE YOUR POSITION.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">By all means, escape the tragedy of an unlived life.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">-J.O.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">By John Obidi | CEO Head Start Africa</div>', 'posts/December2019/F17m7c5UbSmQ9xXF2k1l.jpg', 'renegotiate-your-destiny', 'Renegotiating your destiny by John obidi', 'Renegotiating your destiny by John obidi', 'PUBLISHED', 1, '2019-12-30 17:01:09', '2019-12-30 17:01:09');
