(446, 'Infinix HOT 7 PRO (X625C)', 'infinix-hot-7-pro-x625c-ziksales', '6.2\" HD+ NOTCH - 32GB ROM + 2GB RAM -13MP/2MP + 13MP/2MP- 4000MAH - 4G LTE-black', 36500, '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">6.2\" HD+ NOTCH</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">32GB ROM + 2GB RAM</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">13MP/2MP + 13MP/2MP</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">4000MAH BATTERY</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">ANDROID 9 .0 PIE</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">4G LTE</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">MT6757CD PROCESSOR</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: Ubuntu; font-size: 16px;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; display: inline-block; text-decoration-line: none; color: #00000