; padding: 0px 0px 5px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--mtxt-color); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: var(--hd-ls); outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: var(--hd-fs);\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"_hd\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 5px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--mtxt-color); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: var(--hd-ls); outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: var(--hd-fs);\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"_hd\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 5px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--mtxt-color); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: var(--hd-ls); outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: var(--hd-fs);\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"_hd\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 5px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--mtxt-color); font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: var(--hd-ls); outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: var(--hd-fs);\">Tecno Phantom 9 Summary</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px; line-height: var(--ptxt-lh); font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: #000000;\">Tecno Phantom 9 smartphone was launched on 10th July 2019. The phone comes with a 6.40-inch touchscreen display with a resolution of 1080x2340 pixels at a pixel density of 403 pixels per inch (PPI) and an aspect ratio of 19.5:9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px 0px 15px; outline: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlig