-box;\">Intuitive Gestures</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">Rather than a home button, your iPhone X works with gestures which make navigation simple and fluid. A simple swipe takes you home from anywhere.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/b1f07fbadecab1d4ad3c1b334b113184.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/d91f23cc1c6f1b76921ded5cac0e1229.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">OLED Screen, iPhone Standards</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/1325b3a52c5ce7656b8b0f86630a51ed.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">iPhone X features the iPhone\'s first OLED screen which delivers true stunning colors, deeper blacks, high brightness, and a 1,000,000 to 1 contrast ratio.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Camera</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">The iPhone X\'s TrueDepth camera is housed in a tiny space. The TrueDepth Camera enables Face ID, and let\'s not forget fantastic clarity in images.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Portrait Mode Selfies</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/f9c85771d3986495b18a21c5a72ae995.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">Portrait Mode Selfies allow you to create beautiful selfies with artfully blurred backgrounds and sharp foregrounds.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Portrait Lighting</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/05cf85e540eb27b6a1ffd108f9f5c671.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">With Portrait Lighting, your portraits will have impressive studio-quality lighting effects.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Animoji: Your Emoji</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">The TrueDepth camera analyses more than 50 different muscle movements and uses your expressions to create 12 different Animoji. Reveal your inner Panda, Pig or Robot.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">DUAL 12MP CAMERAS</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/91307c40a54f4d18faab6a2d29e74967.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Improved cameras, better photography&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">With a larger and faster 12MP sensor, new color filters, deeper pixels, and a new telephoto camera with OIS, there\'s so much more you can do with your iPhone X Camera.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Dual Camera, Dual OIS</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/2d4704a011e035f400cbe1f76240ac7a.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">Both 12MP rear cameras feature optical image stabilization and fast lenses so you can capture breathtaking moments (photo and videos) even in low light.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Glass All-Over</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/5e59935dc7a1cb27baaa4f9004d6f36a.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">iPhone X features the most durable glass ever in a smartphone. With glass on the front and back and surgical-grade stainless steel, iPhone X gets even better, thanks to wireless charging. Live free with water and dust resistance (with a rating of IP67).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Face ID: Facial Recognition at its best</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/2056e299e3e074dc77273a8de82da739.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">Face ID provides secure authentication, using your face. Facial Mapping, enabled by the TrueDepth camera, projects and analyzes more than 30k invisible dots on your face to create a precise depth map of your face. Adaptive Recognition means that your Face ID adapts to physical changes in your appearance over time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">PROCESSOR</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; display: block; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ng.jumia.is/cms/external/pet/AP044ELHAC7ENAFAMZ/039e61ebe8c988f7e6c8e8c1eae8e335.jpg\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">iPhone X uses A11 Bionic, the smartest and most powerful chip ever in a smartphone. It features a neural engine capable of 600 billion operations per second. The four efficiency cores in the A11 are 70% faster than A10 Fusion. And the two performance cores are up to 25 percent faster. A11 Bionic powers extraordinary augmented reality experiences in games and apps.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Improved Power Efficiency</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">The custom battery design and a second-generation performance controller allow your phone battery lasts up to 2 hours longer between charges than iPhone 7.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Wireless Charging</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">Designed for the future, iPhone X allows you to charge your phones without charging cables required. Charge with wireless charging stations and mats.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: 