cy, you can fully enjoy the world&rsquo;s most personal device.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Features include:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&bull; VoiceOver &bull; Zoom &bull; Magnifier &bull; Software TTY &bull; Switch Control &bull; Closed Captions &bull; AssistiveTouch &bull; Speak Screen</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Headphones</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">EarPods with Lightning Connector</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">SIM Card</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Nano-SIM</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">iPhone X is not compatible with existing micro-SIM cards.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Rating for Hearing Aids</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">iPhone X (Model A1865, A1901): M3, T4</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">System Requirements</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Apple ID (required for some features)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Internet access10</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Syncing with iTunes on a Mac or PC requires:</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Mac: OS X 10.9.5 or later</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">PC: Windows 7 or later</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">iTunes 12.7 or later (free download from iTunes)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" /><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Environmental Requirements</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: b