: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">Clean, safe and up-to-date</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">Android 8.1.&nbsp;Oreo (version Go) has no unnecessary applications or hidden processes that consume the battery and phone memory.</li>\r\n<li class=\"mezera\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">Exterior</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">5.5 \"HD screen with a 16: 9 aspect ratio</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">Dual front speakers</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">Rear 8MP autofocus camera</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">Front camera 5MP</li>\r\n<li class=\"mezera\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li class=\"mezera\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3px 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: bord