lor: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">RAM: 3 GB</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">ROM: 32 GB (plus up to 512 GB expandable storage via micro SD, not standard)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">*Due to limitations in CPU processing power, memory used by the operating system and pre-installed applications, the actual space available to users may be less than the stated memory capacity. Actual memory space may change due to application updates, user operations, and other related factors.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">NETWORK</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Bluetooth 4.2</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">802.11 b/g/n 2.4 GHz</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Dual SIM</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Dual 4G</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">HUAWEI Share 2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">CONNECTIVITY</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">USB 2.0</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">CAMERA</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Rear Camera: 13 MP + 2 MP (f/1.8) AI</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">Front Camera: 16 MP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">BATTERY</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">4000 mAh (Typical Value)*</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">*Typical value. Actual capacity may vary slightly.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />&nbsp;This capacity is the nominal battery capacity. The actual battery capacity for each individual phone may be slightly above or below the nominal battery capacity.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">CHARGING</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">5V / 2A</li>\r\n</ul>', 'buy Huawei y7 prime online', 400, 1500, 1, 5, 'products/November2019/BI4nKmsHy9cl94tPctwo.jpg', NULL, '2', 0, '2019-11-01 16:33:14', '2019-11-01 16:33:14'),
(487, 'Huawei P30 Lite', 'huawei-p30-lite-ziksales', '6.15-Inch (6GB RAM + 128GB ROM) Android 9.0,48MP + 8MP + 2MP, Dual SIM - Peacock Blue', 126500, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Huawei P30 Lite mobile features a 6.15\" (15.62 cm) display</strong>&nbsp;with a screen resolution of 1080 x 2312 pixels and runs on Android v9.0 (Pie) operating system. The device is powered by Octa-core (2.2 GHz, Quad-core, Cortex A73 + 1.7 GHz, Quad-core, Cortex A53) processor paired with 6GB of RAM. As far as the battery is concerned it has 3340 mAh. Over that, as far as the rear camera is concerned this mobile has a 24MP + 8MP + 2MP camera BSI Sensor supporting a resolution of 5288 x 3968 Pixels and the front snapper is powered by a BSI Sensor. Other sensors include Light sensor, Proximity sensor, Accelerometer, Compass, Gyroscope. So, does it have a fingerprint sensor? Yes, it does. For graphical performance that can make games run smoothly, this phone has got a Mali-G51 MP4 GPU. Onboard storage is at 128GB with the option to expand the memory by Yes Up to 512 GB. Design is one of the most important factors when it comes to mobiles. This phone is 7.4 mm slim thickness and weighs 159 grams.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; color: #282828; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif;\">To understand how the cameras work so well on the P30 Lite, there are some technicalities that must be laid out. With the P30 Lite, Huawei has equipped a completely new color filter in the camera. Instead of the Red, Green, Green, Blue (RGGB) Bayer Pattern filter that we see being in almost every camera sensors, it uses a Red, Yellow, Yellow, Blue (RYYB) filter pattern, which is claimed to help it capture 40% more light, which is achieved due to this Yellow subpixels as they are said to absorb both Red and Greenlight.</p>', 'buy Huawei p30 lite online', 400, 2000, 1, 5, 'products/November2019/D8slE384oOIPnRGNuCtZ.jpg', '[\"products\\/November2019\\/GMAWhbzjiB4W0r0K6Hz1.jpg\"]', '2', 0, '2019-11-01 16:37:03', '2019-11-01 16:37:03');
